descriptionHtml:
My female Breton Norie Skal, Level 1. Game saved quite at the beginning of the game in the middle of Bleak Falls Barrow.

Hope you like her.

- Calientes Female Body Mod Big Bottom Edition CBBE v0.2: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666#content

- No more blocky faces v1.5 by Xenius: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=30
- High Quality Eyes v1.2 by Xenius: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=498
- Weathered Warpaint and Improved Dirt v1.1 by Xenius: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=4489
- Detailed faces v2.0 by Xenius: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=26

Mods used at the cloth on the screenshots:
- Killer Keos Skimpy CBBE Armor Set v3-5, mage appearence robe replacement: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=3654#content
- Nocturnal Ghost Clothes -CBBE version- v0.2 by Ryhpez: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=3254#content (replaced a wedding dress, just for the screenshot)

Greetings, 
Kilmantor
